      <pubDate>Mon, 19 Feb 2024 15:34:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>Forvia 将裁员 10,000 人，以更好地参与电动汽车转型</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-19/forvia-to-cut-10-000-jobs-to-better-compete-in-ev-transition</link>
      <description><![CDATA[汽车零部件供应商 Forvia SE 准备在未来五年内裁员约 13% 的欧洲员工，并计划利用人工智能在转向电动汽车的过程中更好地与亚洲竞争对手竞争。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-19/forvia-to-cut-10-000-jobs-to-better-compete-in-ev-transition</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 19 Feb 2024 09:29:12 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>印度农民暂停抗议以审查政府农作物协议</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-19/indian-farmers-pause-protests-to-review-government-crop-deal</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在与政府进行最新一轮谈判后，印度农民暂停了抗议活动，尽管一部分种植者不同意拟议的协议。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-19/indian-farmers-pause-protests-to-review-government-crop-deal</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 19 Feb 2024 02:43:13 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
